    • createSession

      public Statistics createSession(List<String> studentUsernames, int totalTimeInSessions, int streak, int totalQuestions, int totalQuestionsRight, int totalQuestionsWrong, int sessionsCompleted, int daysLoggedIn, int subjectMasteryValue, float guessRate, float avgTimeSpentInSession, float successRate, float avgTimePerQuestion)
      Creates a new session for a student.
      Parameters:
      studentUsernames - The list of student usernames.
      totalTimeInSessions - The total time spent in sessions.
      streak - The user's current streak.
      totalQuestions - The total number of questions answered.
      totalQuestionsRight - The total number of questions answered correctly.
      totalQuestionsWrong - The total number of questions answered incorrectly.
      sessionsCompleted - The total number of sessions completed.
      daysLoggedIn - The total number of days the user has logged in.
      subjectMasteryValue - The user's subject mastery value.
      guessRate - The user's guess rate.
      avgTimeSpentInSession - The average time spent in a session.
      successRate - The user's success rate.
      avgTimePerQuestion - The average time spent per question.
      Returns:
      The created session statistics.
